org.apache.poi.sl.usermodel

Interface ObjectShape<S extends Shape<S,P>,P extends TextParagraph<S,P,? extends TextRun>>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    PlaceableShape<S,P>, Shape<S,P>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HSLFObjectShape, XSLFObjectShape 

    public interface ObjectShape<S extends Shape<S,P>,P extends TextParagraph<S,P,? extends TextRun>>
extends Shape<S,P>, PlaceableShape<S,P>
    An shape which references an embedded OLE object(引用嵌入的OLE对象的形状)
    Since:
    POI 4.0.0

      • getProgId

        java.lang.String getProgId()
        Returns the ProgID that stores the OLE Programmatic Identifier. A ProgID is a string that uniquely identifies a given object, for example, "Word.Document.8" or "Excel.Sheet.8".(返回存储PLE编程标识符的ProgID。ProgID是唯一标识给定对象的字符串，例如“Word.Document.8”或“Excel.Sheet.8”。)
        Returns:
        the ProgID(的ProgID)

      • getFullName

        java.lang.String getFullName()
        Returns the full name of the embedded object, e.g. "Microsoft Word Document" or "Microsoft Office Excel Worksheet".(返回嵌入对象的全名，例如“Microsoft Word Document”或“Microsoft Office Excel收件箱”。)
        Returns:
        the full name of the embedded object(嵌入对象的全名)

      • updateObjectData

        java.io.OutputStream updateObjectData(ObjectMetaData.Application application,
                                      ObjectMetaData metaData)
                               throws java.io.IOException
        Updates the ole data. If there wasn't an object registered before, a new ole embedding is registered in the parent slideshow.

        For HSLF this needs to be a POIFSFileSystem stream.

        (更新ole数据。如果之前没有注册对象，则会在父幻灯片中注册新的ole嵌入。对于HSLF，这需要是POIFSFileSystem流。)
        Parameters:
        application - a preset application enum(应用程序-预设的应用程序列举)
        metaData - or a custom metaData object, can be null if the application has been set(metaData -或自定义metaData对象，如果已设置应用程序，则可以为空)
        Returns:
        an OutputStream which receives the new data, the data will be persisted on close()(接收新数据的OutputStream，数据将在close（）时持久化)
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - if the linked object data couldn't be found or a new object data couldn't be initialized(java.io. IOResponse-如果找不到链接的对象数据或无法初始化新对象数据)

      • readObjectData

        default java.io.InputStream readObjectData()
                                    throws java.io.IOException
        Reads the ole data as stream - the application specific stream is served The raw data serves the outer/wrapped object, which is usually a POIFSFileSystem stream, whereas this method return the unwrapped entry(将ole数据读取为流-服务特定于应用程序的流原始数据服务于外部/包装对象，该对象通常是POIFSFileSystem流，而此方法返回未包装的条目)
        Returns:
        an InputStream which serves the object data(提供对象数据的InputStream)
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - if the linked object data couldn't be found(java.io. IOResponse-如果找不到链接的对象数据)
